trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls used for editing the properties, layout, appearance, and behavior of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller som brukes til å redigere egenskapene, oppsettet, utseendet og virkemåten for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The EditorPartCollection class is a read-only collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls, typically used by an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone to track the set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls contained by the zone.
trans-unit.target: Klassen EditorPartCollection er en skrivebeskyttet samling <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller, som vanligvis brukes av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>sone for å spore sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller av sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: When a Web Parts page enters edit mode, and a user selects a control to edit, the editing process begins.
trans-unit.target: Når en webdeler side angir redigeringsmodus, og brukeren velger en kontroll for redigering, begynner redigering prosessen.

trans-unit.source: The zone creates a new EditorPartCollection object consisting of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls contained by the zone.
trans-unit.target: Sonen oppretter et nytt EditorPartCollection-objekt som består av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller av sonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: At various phases in the editing process, the zone accesses the EditorPartCollection object to save or retrieve property values between the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in the collection and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control currently being edited.
trans-unit.target: Sonen gir tilgang til EditorPartCollection-objektet for å lagre eller henter egenskapsverdier mellom i ulike faser pågår redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller i samlingen og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollere blir redigert.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: You can create an EditorPartCollection collection of controls for your own programmatic use if, for example, you need to perform some mass operation on a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Du kan opprette en EditorPartCollection samling av kontroller for programmatisk Bruk Hvis for eksempel må du utføre noen for operasjonen på et sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Even though the EditorPartCollection object is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Selv om EditorPartCollection-objektet er skrivebeskyttet, kan du endre programmatisk egenskapene for de underliggende kontrollene det refereres til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en tom ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The EditorPartCollection constructor initializes an empty instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren EditorPartCollection initialiserer en tom forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: This overload of the constructor is used internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> class in its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.CreateEditorParts%2A> method to create an empty collection object.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren-overlasten er brukt internt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>klasse i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.CreateEditorParts%2A>metode for å opprette en tom samling-objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: The zone then creates instances of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls declared in the child zone template, and uses an internal method to add them to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Sonen deretter opprettes forekomster av alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller deklarert i malen underordnede sone og bruker en intern metode til å legge dem til i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: You cannot use this overload of the EditorPartCollection constructor to create a new instance of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> and add <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to it.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ikke bruke denne overlasten EditorPartCollection-konstruktøren for å opprette en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>og legge til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller til det.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: You must use one of the other overloads for the EditorPartCollection constructor instead.
trans-unit.target: Du må bruke en annen overlastingene for EditorPartCollection konstruktøren i stedet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> class by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> klasse ved å sende i en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The EditorPartCollection constructor initializes an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> class and passes in a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren EditorPartCollection initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>klassen og formidler i en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: This is one overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor that you can use to create a new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object and add <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to it.
trans-unit.target: Dette er én overbelastning av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør som du kan bruke til å opprette en ny <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objekt, og Legg til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller til det.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Even though the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> instance created by the constructor is read-only, you can still access the individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in the collection programmatically and call their properties and methods.
trans-unit.target: Selv om den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>forekomster opprettet i konstruktøren er skrivebeskyttet, kan du fortsatt tilgang til individuelle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollerer i samlingen programmatisk og kall sine egenskaper og metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: One common scenario for using the EditorPartCollection constructor would be if you want to perform some batch operation on an entire set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls, such as changing the content, appearance, or position of a related group of them.
trans-unit.target: Er en vanlig scenario for å bruke EditorPartCollection konstruktøren Hvis du vil utføre en bunke-operasjon på en hele settet med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller, for eksempel endre innhold, utseendet eller plasseringen av en beslektet gruppe dem.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Another common scenario for using the EditorPartCollection constructor is developing custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls that you want to associate with a server control, so that users can edit custom properties on your control.
trans-unit.target: En annen vanlig scenario for å bruke EditorPartCollection konstruktøren utvikler egendefinerte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller som du vil knytte til et serverkontroll slik at brukere kan redigere egendefinerte egenskaper for kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: In this scenario, your server control must implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable> interface, and as part of that task, it must implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: I dette scenarioet din serverkontroll må implementere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable>grensesnittet, og som en del av oppgaven, må den implementere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable>

trans-unit.source: In that method, to enable the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to edit your server control, you must add the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> instance, such as an <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> object.
trans-unit.target: I dette metode for å aktivere egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller til å redigere serverkontroll, må du legge til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller til en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>serverforekomsten som en <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>objektet.</xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> </xref:System.Collections.ICollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Then you can pass the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor to create a new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object, which the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone uses to set up all the controls and begin the editing process.
trans-unit.target: Deretter kan du sende samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection.%23ctor%2A>konstruktøren for å opprette en ny <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objektet, som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>sone bruker til å definere alle kontrollene og begynner prosessen for redigering.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> class by passing in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls, and an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of additional <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> klasse ved å sende i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller, og en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling av flere <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of existing <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls in a zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>for eksisterende <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller i en sone.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls not in a zone, but created programmatically.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller ikke i en sone, men opprettes programmatisk.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Returns a value that indicates whether a particular control is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om en bestemt kontroll i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method determines whether a specific <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> control is already in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Contains bestemmer om en bestemt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollen er allerede i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> being tested for its status as a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> som testes for statusen som et medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Kopierer samlingen til en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to create a custom array that can contain the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object, a subset of those controls, or a superset of those controls.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo er nyttig når du vil opprette en egendefinert matrise kan inneholde den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>objekt, et delsett av kontrollene og overordnet kontrollene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> to contain the copied collection of controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> skal inneholde kopierte samlingen av kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: Startpunktet i matrisen som skal plasseres samlingen innholdet.

trans-unit.source: References a static, read-only, empty instance of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Refererer til en statisk skrivebeskyttet, tom forekomst av samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A static, read-only, empty instance of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> reduces memory usage in cases where you want an empty collection instance to return the proper object type from a method or to compare the instance with another object, but you do not need to add members to the instance.
trans-unit.target: En statisk skrivebeskyttet, tom forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>reduserer minnebruk i tilfeller der du vil bruke en tom samling forekomst til å returnere riktig objekttypen fra en annen metode, eller til å sammenligne forekomst med et annet objekt, men du trenger ikke å legge til medlemmer i forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer posisjonen for en bestemt medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls on a Web Parts page, and you need to locate a particular control in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IndexOf er nyttig hvis du har flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller i en webdeler, og du trenger å finne en bestemt kontroll i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> som et medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An integer that corresponds to the index of an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som samsvarer med indeksen for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a specific member of the collection according to a unique identifier.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et angitt medlem i samlingen i henhold til en unik identifikator.

trans-unit.source: The index of a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> in a collection.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> i en samling.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.
